  "dialog_title_voucher_purchase_success": "%s e-Voucher has been successfully purchased",
  "dialog_message_purchase_voucher_success": "You can find your purchased e-Vouchers in \u201cmy e-Vouchers\u201d section",
  "dialog_message_confirm_voucher_purchase": "Are you sure you want to buy %s e-Voucher for %s JD's",
  "dialog_label_e_voucher_code": "e-Voucher Code",
  "faq_q_1": "What are Electronic Vouchers?",
  "faq_a_1": "Electronic Vouchers are prepaid cards that contain a specific amount of money that anyone can buy to download favorite applications, games, videos or content.",
  "faq_q_2": "How can I pay for Electronic Vouchers I buy from Orange Money?",
  "faq_a_2": "You can pay for the Electronic Vouchers directly through your Orange Money wallet",
  "faq_q_3": "How can I purchase my favorite Electronic Vouchers from Orange Money wallet?",
  "faq_a_3": "You can purchase your favorite Electronic Vouchers from Orange Money wallet by following the below steps:\n\n1.\tLogin to Orange Money Jordan Application\n\n2.\tChoose e-Vouchers tab\n\n3.\tSelect your desired Electronic Voucher from the list or you can filter to easily find the desired Electronic Vouchers then press \u201cNext\u201d\n\n4.\tThen chose the desired Electronic Voucher Store and the denomination and then press more \u201cDetails and Buy\u201d\n\n5.\tThen check the Electronic Voucher details you want to buy, and after reading and accepting the terms and conditions, press \u201cBuy\u201d\n\n6.\tA confirmation screen will appear to confirm the purchase, and the price of the electronic voucher will be shown in Jordanian dinars, which will be deducted from your wallet, then click on \u201cConfirm\u201d\n\n7.\tThen the purchase process will be completed successfully and You will get the code instantly in the screen and you can \u201ccopy\u201d it or \u201cshare\u201d it",
  "faq_q_4": "How can I find all the Electronic Vouchers that I purchased in Orange Money application?",
  "faq_a_4": "You can find all your Electronic Vouchers that you purchased in \u201cMy e-Vouchers\u201d tab",
  "faq_q_5": "How can I see the details of a certain Electronic Vouchers I purchased from Orange Money application? ",
  "faq_a_5": "You can find the details for the electronic Vouchers that you purchased in \u201cMy e-Vouchers\u201d tab and you can see the details by clicking \u201cMore details\u201d",
  "faq_q_6": "What if I purchased an Electronic Voucher but it didn\u2019t appear in my Electronic Vouchers list?",
  "faq_a_6": "Please call 1441 from Orange or 0777700141 from other networks ",
  "faq_q_7": "What if i purchased an Electronic Voucher but couldn\u2019t redeem it on the desired platform? ",
  "faq_a_7": "Please call 1441 from Orange or 0777700141 from other networks and we will be more than happy to help you",
  "faq_q_8": "What is the difference between denomination and price? ",
  "faq_a_8": "Denomination is the value that you will find in your account when you redeem your Electronic Voucher on the respective platform; the price is the Electronic Voucher value in Jordanian Dinars",
  "faq_q_9": "What are the unique features of Orange Money Electronic Vouchers?",
  "faq_a_9": "\u2022\tOrange Money Electronic Vouchers are available 24/7.\n\n\u2022\tThe process is very simple and secure. No complicated steps to follow.\n\n\u2022\tCustomer will get the desired Electronic Vouchers directly and instantly after the purchase",
  "faq_q_10": "What are the Electronic Voucher types available?",
  "faq_a_10": "\u2022\tiTunes cards for apple app store \n\n\u2022\tGoogle Play\n\n\u2022\tPlayStation Network\n\n\u2022\tNintendo eShop \n\n\u2022\tXbox \n\n\u2022\tSteam\n\n\u2022\tRixty \n\n\u2022\tSpotify\n\n\u2022\tPUBG\n\n\u2022\tAmazon\n\n\u2022\tLeague of Legends\n\n\u2022\teBay \n",
  "faq_q_11": "Does an Electronic Voucher expire?",
  "faq_a_11": "Expiry of Electronic Vouchers is 6 months from purchasing time",
  "faq_q_12": "What is the currency used to pay for Electronic Vouchers?",
  "faq_a_12": "The currency used is Jordanian Dinars",
  "faq_q_13": "Will the Electronic Voucher code work if I bought it from a different account store other than the one I use for my account?",
  "faq_a_13": "No, when the Electronic Voucher is purchased in a different account store, the Electronic Voucher code will not work",
