  "title_ramadan_charity": "Help people in need through Orange Money",
  "charity_desc": "\"Let us help deliver your Zakat and Sadaqa to those in need. Now you can donate to several trusted charities through the Orange Money wallet. Orange Money will\u00a0contribute with up to 3 JD\u2019s from your donation amount to the same charity\"",
  "orange_services_desc": "\"Every time you refill your Orange prepaid lines or pay your Orange Postpaid bills in Ramadan via Orange Money Wallet, you'll get a free 10 GB bundle.\"",
  "orange_services_desc2": "\u2022 The bundle will be granted for refills above 5\n \u00a0\u00a0JD denomination and bill payments above 5\n \u00a0\u00a0JD\u2019s throught the \"Orange Services\" icon\n \u00a0\u00a0\u00a0inside Orange Money App\n \u2022 To check the bundle remaining balance and\n \u00a0\u00a0\u00a0expiry date, dial *355#\n \u2022 The bundle is valid for 7 days",
  "title_orange_services": "Pay for Orange Services & Get 10 GB",
  "btn_buy_now": "Buy Now",
  "ramadan_bundle_desc": "Special offer to Orange Money customers, stay connected with your loved ones and all that matters to you with our Ramadan Internet Bundle. Get 10 GB for 1 JD ONLY",
  "ramadan_bundle_desc2": "\u2022 To check the bundle remaining balance and\n \u00a0\u00a0\u00a0expiry date, dial *355#\n\u2022 The bundle is valid for 7 days",
  "title_ramadan_bundle": "10 GB for 1 JD",
  "btn_shop_now": "Shop Now",
  "e_shops_desc": "With every purchased device or Smart Life Kit from Orange eShop in Ramadan, you\u2019ll get a 20 JD\u2019s Carrefour voucher and a free Orange Money Visa Card.",
  "open_wallet_desc": "Open your Orange Money wallet and get a free 3GB bundle, valid for one week.",
  "open_wallet_term_cond": "\u2022 The bundle is valid for Orange mobile customers only\n\n\n\u2022 A minimum amount of 5 JD has to be cashed in the wallet to get the free internet bundle\n\n\n\u2022 To check the bundle remaining balance and expiry date, dial  *355# ",
  "title_open_wallet": "Open your free Orange Money Wallet & Get 3 GB",
  "title_dandana": "Subscribe to Dandana service & get the chance to win 100 JD\u2019s",
  "dandana_desc": "Enter a draw to win 100 JD\u2019s when you subscribe to Dandana service & change your mobile tone, call 090090900 or visit dandana.orange.com to choose your new ring back tone.",
  "dandana_term_cond": "\u2022 Service fee: 20 piasters/week. \n\u2022 Number of winners: 4 \n\u2022 Competition duration: 12/4/2021-17/5/2021 \n\u2022 The cash prizes will be cashed into the\n \u00a0\u00a0winners\u2019 Orange Money Wallets.",
  "emani_desc": "You can win 500 JD\u2019s when you subscribe to Emani service & listen to the religious content (Holy Quran, Ahadeeth, Dua\u2019a & Nasheed and more) for not less than 5 minutes. Send 1 to 97741 and enter the draw now.",
  "emani_term_cond": "\u2022 Service fee: 9 piasters/day. \n\u2022 Number of winners: 1 \n\u2022 The cash prizes will be cashed into the\n \u00a0\u00a0winners\u2019 Orange Money Wallets \n\u2022 Competition duration: 12/4/2021-17/5/2021",
  "title_emani": "Subscribe to Emani service and get the chance to win 500 JD\u2019s",
  "tikram_desc": "Join the campaign with only 200 points from Tikram eShop and enter the draw for a chance to be one of 4 lucky winners of a 300 JD\u2019s cash prize.",
  "tikram_term_cond": "\u2022 The cash prizes will be cashed into the\n\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0winners\u2019 Orange Money Wallets. \n\u2022 Tickets purchased cannot be refunded or\n \u00a0\u00a0exchanged.\n\u2022 Draws will take place at the end of each\n \u00a0\u00a0Ramadan week. \n\u2022 The more tickets you buy, the higher your\n \u00a0\u00a0chance to win.",
  "title_tikram": "Join our Win with Tikram & get a chance to win 300 JD\u2019s",
  "title_fawanees": "Play Fawanees game and win cash prizes",
  "fawanees_term_cond": "\u2022\tA specific gift will be distributed based on the number of collected Fawanees\n\n\u2022\tEach day there is an opportunity to win one Fanoos\n\n\u2022\tCompetition duration: 30 days of Ramadan 2021\n\n\u2022\tFirst draw: Subscribers who won 10 Fawanees on 27th of April2021 will get into the first raffle automatically, and be one of the 20 lucky winners who will win 100 JD\u2019s cash prizes. The raffle will take place on 29/4/2021.\n\n\u2022\tSecond draw: Subscribers who won 20 Fawanees at the end of Ramadan will get into the second raffle automatically, and be one of the 20 lucky winners who will win 200 JD cash prizes. The raffle will take place on 18/5/2021.\n\n\u2022\tPrizes cashed into Orange Money Wallets\n\n\n",
  "fawanees_desc": "Only with Max it application & during the holy month of Ramadan, we\u2019ll ask you 30 questions and with every correct answer, you get one Fanoos. The goal of collecting Fawanees is passing the games\u2019 4 levels. You will receive immediate prizes and be eligible to enter a draw on cash prizes cased into Orange Money Wallets for 30 lucky winners.",
  "btn_play_now": "Play Now",
