  "remittance_term_and_cond_text": "1) The client acknowledges and agrees to discharge Petra Mobile Payment Services Company (Orange Money) and its correspondents, agents, members and employees from any responsibilities or losses caused by the beneficiary\u2019s bank rejection to receive transfer amount for any reason not related to Petra Mobile Payment Services Company (Orange Money).\n\n    \n \n2)Petra Mobile Payment Services Company (Orange Money) at its discretion shall have the right to make use of any correspondent or agent to effect transfer of funds on behalf of its clients and shall not be liable for any of its correspondents or shall be held liable for any loss or damage resulting from any interruptions , delays ,errors ,omission, mutations occurring in the mail ,telex, wire cable or swift services on the part of any postal and telegraph authority or resulting from circumstances .\n\n    \n \n3)The client acknowledges and agrees that Petra Mobile Payment Services Company (Orange Money) shall not be liable in case funds are blocked due to the embargo economic situations or any other reasons.\n\n    \n \n4) It is understand that the beneficiary may not obtain the full value due to exchange rate, fees or charges applicable in the country or to paying bank or the correspondent banks.\n\n\n    \n \n5) The beneficiary bank ( BIC / Sort Code / Fed wire ID / IBAN or any such Code ) mentioned by the remitter will be considered as accurate and remittance will be effected accordingly , assuming correctness of the given codes without any liabilities or responsibilities on Petra Mobile Payment Services Company (Orange Money) and if there are any amendments or cancellation .THE charges will be poured by the client .\n\n    \n \n6)If the client requests a refund of a transfer , such a refund will be made only if the receiving party agrees to that payment of funds has not been effected to the beneficiary and funds are retuned by our correspondent or agent. If the amount is in foreign currency refund will be made in Jordanian dinars at the prevailing buying rate at the time of refund after deducting our fees and our correspondents or agents\u2019 fees and charges.\n\n    \n \n7)Payment of transferred funds is subject to the rules and regulations of the country where the payment is to be made. Petra Mobile Payment Services Company (Orange Money) or its correspondents or agents shall not be held liable for any loss or delay in payment caused on account of any act or order of government agency or any other conditions.\n\n\n    8)Remittance are subject to the laws relating to monetary transaction in Jordan / intermediary / designated countries.\n\n    \n \n9)Details / purpose of payment with complete remitter & beneficiary address ( including street , city , country and contacts) are mandatory on all transfer and demanded draft applications submitted to Petra Mobile Payment Services Company (Orange Money) in order to process the transaction in case required information is not sufficient. Petra Mobile Payment Services Company (Orange Money) also reserve the right to decline /  delay and /or report any payment requests without any liability on the part of the Petra Mobile Payment Services Company (Orange Money) if it is of the opinion that the information does not meet any act or order of a regulatory / government authority . Petra Mobile Payment Services Company (Orange Money) may take  any action , in its sole and absolute discretion , which it considers appropriate to take in accordance with all laws and regulations including , but not limited to the prevention of money laundering and/or terrorism financing and will not held liable for any loss / damages suffered by any party arising out of any of these actions.\n\n\n    \n \n10)Petra Mobile Payment Services Company (Orange Money) may have the right to decline to make a payment, if it believes that involves a breach by any person / entity of a law or regulation of any country. A payment may be delayed or declined because a person / entity involved in the payment or an authority requires information or clarification in compliance with the law or regulations or declines to process it. Petra Mobile Payment Services Company (Orange Money) will share information of your remittance as necessary.\n\n\n    \n \n11)No financial claim can be made by the beneficiary / beneficiaries after any amount received.\n\n\n    \n \n12)The sender / recipient will be fully responsible to provides necessary evidence, legality, clarification , source of fund clarification and additional information about identification to prove geniality , legality of entities funds involved and for the purpose of follow up with concerned authorities and for effecting payment or refund as the case may be.\n\n\n    \n \n13)The sender / recipient confirms and agrees to provide Petra Mobile Payment Services Company (Orange Money) with valid and up to date identity purpose of transfer and the source of funds documents upon requests or other additional deemed pertinent to comply with laws related to monetary transaction in the Hashemite kingdom of Jordan / intermediary /destined countries requirement or as may otherwise require to comply with regulatory or other legal obligations.\n\n    \n \n14)The sender /recipient will only act on his own behalf he may not submit or receive a transaction on behalf of third parties if he intends to submit or receive a transaction on behalf of third party he must first inform Petra Mobile Payment Services Company (Orange Money) of his desire to do so and provide us with any additional information about it which wills help as request in order that we may decide whether to permit or reject the transaction .\n\n\n\n    \n \n15) The sender /  recipient of this transfer confirms and knows that this absolutely prohibited and will not be processed if the transfer was linked to an individual or body or state that are forbidden to be dealt with or they were mentioned in the banned lists that are issued by the competent.\n\n\n    \n \n16)Such general terms and conditions shall be governed by the provisions and laws applicable in Jordan.\n    Jordanian court shall be competent to settle any disputes arising from this contract. In case of any dispute over the interpretation of the English provision here of and its addend the Arabic provision shall be the reference.\n\n    \n \n17) International remittance service provided by Petra Mobile Payment Services Company (Orange Money) is in collaboration with Musharabsh Exchange\n\n    \n \n18) The customer acknowledges and agrees to share his data with the third party (Musharbash Exchange)\n   ",
