  "title_sweet_shop": "Discount at many sweets shops & restaurants when you pay through Orange Money wallet",
  "ramadan_offers_financial_transaction": "Use Orange Money wallet to get a chance to enter a draw to win Samsung devices and Cash Backs",
  "ramadan_offers_eshop": "Make purchases at Orange eShop using your Orange Money wallet and get 25% Cash Back",
  "ramadan_offers_fiber": "Subscribe to Fiber and open an Orange Money wallet & Cash In 1 JD or more to get 10 JD\u2019s Cash Back ",
  "ramadan_offers_postpaid": "Buy an Orange Postpaid line and open an Orange Money wallet with a 1 JD Cash In or more to get Cash Back of the line issuance fees",
  "terms_and_conditions_apply": null,
  "terms_cond_bill_payment": "\"\u2022\tThe offer is valid for 077 or 0707 Orange Mobile holders. The Internet Bundle will be added to the number that is linked to the wallet, through which the payment was made.\n\u2022\tThe Added internet Bundle is valid for one week.\n\u2022\tThe beneficiary Orange Line must be active on the network for at least 30 days in order to receive the promotional Bundle.\n\u2022\tThe accepted transactions for the promotional offer are Orange Prepaid Refills and Orange Postpaid Bill Payments made through the \"Orange Services\" icon that is available inside Orange Money wallet.\n\u2022\tThe Refill face value must be 5 JD's or above and the value of the Bill Payment must be 5 JD's or above per transaction to get the promotional bundle.\n\u2022\tThe number of allowed times to benefit from the promotional offer is subject to the maximum number of allowed monthly transactions per customer that is mentioned in [wallet limits and fees] icon.\n\u2022\tTo check the remaining balance and the bundle validity, please press *355#\n\u2022\tThe offer is valid only in Ramadan, and customers will be notified of any updates that may occur to the offer through social media platforms, SMS, or our website.\"",
  "terms_cond_charity": "\"1.\tThis campaign is valid during Ramadan\n2.\tThis campaign includes all the charity organizations inside Charity icon\n3.\tOrange Money will contribute with the same amount of your donation with a maximum 3 JD\u2019s to the same charity\n\"",
  "desc1_sweet_shops": "\"In Ramadan get discount form many sweets shops & restaurants when you pay through Orange Money wallet\"",
  "desc2_sweet_shops": "In Ramadan get discount form many sweets shops when you pay through Orange Money wallet\nShops as follows:\n1. X Shop - X Disount and channel used for payment (Visa or/and money transfer)\n2. X Shop - X Disount and channel used for payment (Visa or/and money transfer)\n3. X Shop - X Disount and channel used for payment (Visa or/and money transfer)",
  "terms_cond_sweet_shops": "\"\u2022\tGreen Salon Sweets :\n\n\u2022\tCustomers will get 10% discount in all Green Salon Sweets Branches On all items except (Konafa, Aleppo mix, Aleppo mix with cashew , Warbat with nuts , Algerian)\n\u2022\tThis offer is valid only in Ramadan\n\u2022\tYou must pay with Orange Money Visa Card to get the discount\n\u2022\tGreen Salon Sweets Branches:\n\u2022\tJarash - Bab amman\n\u2022\tJarash \u2013 Downtown\n\u2022\tAjloun Main Street\n\u2022\tKufranja - Ghor Street\n\u2022\tBaqaa - Downtown\n\u2022\tBaqa - dwar alshuwuwn\n\u2022\tMafraq \u2013 Downtown\n\u2022\tShweika - Aidoun Street\n\u2022\tSalt - alsarw\n\n\n\u2022\tArafat Sweets :\n\n\u2022\tCustomers will get 10% discount in Arafat Sweets On all items except (Konafa, anything with cheese, baklawa)\n\u2022\tThis offer is valid only in Ramadan\n\u2022\tYou must pay with Orange Money Visa Card to get the discount\n\u2022\tArafat Sweets Branches:\n\u2022\tAmman \u2013 Madina al mnowara street\n\n\u2022\tPapakanafa  :\n\n\u2022\tCustomers will get 10% discount in Papakanafa On all items\n\u2022\tThis offer is valid only in Ramadan\n\u2022\tYou must pay with Orange Money Visa Card to get the discount\n\u2022\tPapakanafa Branches:\n\u2022\t Madina al mnowara street\n\u2022\tAbdoun\n\n\u2022\t39ertime  :\n\n\u2022\tCustomers will get 10% discount in 39ertime On all items\n\u2022\tThis offer is valid only in Ramadan\n\u2022\tYou must pay with Orange Money Visa Card to get the discount\n\u2022\t39ertime Branches:\n\u2022\t Madina al mnowara street\n\u2022\tAbdoun\n\u2022\tMecca street\n\n\n\n\u2022\tLebnani Snack:\n\n\u2022\tCustomers will get many offers in Lebnani Snack branchers as below:\n\n\u2022\tFirst Offer: Any two liters of Ramadan juice (lemonade, dates, Karkadeh, julep) only for 2.50 JD\n\u2022\tSecond Offer: Any French sandwich of your choice with fries and Pepsi only for 2.75 JD\n\u2022\tThird Offer: 8 broasted pieces, fries, garlic, bread and a liter of Pepsi only for 5.90\n\u2022\tFourth Offer: Suhoor for two people Pottery and cheese manoucheh with Zattar, two cups of tea, bread and an appetizer plate for only 7 JD\n\n\u2022\tThis offer is valid from 28-03-2022 till end of Ramadan\n\u2022\tYou must pay with Orange Money Visa Card to get the discount\n\u2022\tShmeisani\n\u2022\tSweifieh\n\u2022\tUniversity street\n\u2022\tAbdoun\n\u2022\tAbdali\n\u2022\tMecca Mall\n\u2022\tMarka\n\u2022\tRadio Street\n\u2022\tAqaba\n\n\n\u2022\tBeirut Catering Services:\n\n\u2022\tCustomers will get many offers in Beirut Catering Services as below:\n\u2022\tFirst Offer : Any Sider 3 chickens and your choice (mandi, ouzi, freekeh, biryani , kabseh ) 28 JD including tax\n\u2022\tSecond offer : A pot of grape leaves for 6 people  only for  38 JD including tax instead of 52 JD\n\u2022\tThird Offer : Order any romanian beef Sider 3 KG  (mansaf, ouzi, qedreh) only for 45 JD including tax instead of 54 JD\n\n\u2022\tThis offer is valid from 28-03-2022 till end of Ramadan\n\u2022\tYou must pay with Orange Money Visa Card to get the discount\n\n\n\u2022\tDivan Cake :\n\n\u2022\tCustomers will get 15% discount in Divan cake\n\u2022\tThis offer is valid only in Ramadan\n\u2022\tYou must pay with Orange Money Visa Card to get the discount\n\u2022\tDivan cake branches:\n\u2022\tAlgardens\n\u2022\tJabal alhussain\n\n\n\u2022\tFantastic Cake :\n\n\u2022\tCustomers will get 10% discount in Fantastic cake\n\u2022\tThis offer is valid only in Ramadan\n\u2022\tYou must pay with Orange Money Visa Card to get the discount\n\u2022\tFantastic cake branches:\n\u2022\tMarj al hamam\n\n\n\u2022\tJeetbwaktk Restaurants :\n\n\u2022\tCustomers will get 10% discount before iftar and 25% after iftar on all items in all Jeetbwaktk Restaurants branches\n\u2022\tThis offer is valid only in Ramadan\n\u2022\tYou must pay with Orange Money Visa Card to get the discount\n\u2022\tJeetbwaktk Restaurants branches:\n\u2022\tIrbid Baghdad street Albareed Circle\n\u2022\tIrbid Madeineh Senaeyh circle\n\u2022\tIrbid Al Jamaa\u2019 street- Eskan light\n\u2022\tIrbid \u2013 Opposite to Al Hasan sport city\n\u2022\tIrbid Al durra circle\n\u2022\tIrbid Al huson \u2013 main street\n\u2022\tAjloun -main street\n\u2022\tAlmafraq al Baladyeh street\n\u2022\tJarash near al Qairawan circle\"",
  "desc1_draws": "\"During Ramadan, use Orange Money wallet to:\n1. Refill  your Orange Prepaid line and get a chance to win a Samsung S21 Ultra Device\n2. Pay your Orange Postpaid Bill and get a chance to be one of 20 lucky winners for a full Cash Back of your Bill amount or be the lucky winner of one year Cash Back of your bill amount\n3. Make Orange eShop purchases and get a chance to win a Samsung S21 Ultra Device\n4. Pay utility bills through eFAWATEERcom and get a chance to win a Samsung S21 Ultra Device\"",
  "terms_cond_draws": "\"\u2022 3 Samsung S21 Ultra devices will be drawn in the month of Ramadan as follows:\n    \u2022 Draw on 1 device for customers who refill Orange Prepaid lines through the \"Orange Services\" icon.\n    \u2022 Draw on 1 device for customers who make payments through eFAWATEERcom icon inside Orange Money wallet (except for Orange related payments)\n    \u2022 Draw on 1 device for customers who make purchases from the Orange eShop and pay through the Orange Money wallet\n\u2022 A draw for 20 winners for a full cashback of the value of Orange Postpaid Bill Payment paid through the \u201cOrange services\u201d icon. The maximum cashback value is 25 JD\u2019s.\n\u2022 A draw for one winner to cover the value of his Orange Postpaid bill for 1 full year. Maximum coverage of 300 JD\u2019s where 25 JD's will be cashed into the customers' wallet on monthly basis\n\u2022 Each customer is entitled to win only one of the above prizes.\n\u2022 All the above-mentioned prizes will be randomly drawn and given to winners maximum one working week after Eid Al-Fitr\n\u2022 The value of the payments must be more than 5 JD to enter the above draws\"",
  "desc1_e_shop": "\"In Ramadan, make purchases at Orange eShop using your Orange Money wallet or Orange Money Visa Card and get 25% cashback\"",
  "term_cond_eshop": " \"\u2022 Cashback will be cashed in  after a maximum one working week after Eid Al-Fitr\n\u2022 Transactions included will be payments through Orange Money wallet or Orange Money Visa Cards\n\u2022 Maximum cashback amount is 5 JD\n\u2022 Payment amount must be greater than 5 JDs in order to benefit from the cashback\n\u2022 This offer is only valid during Ramadan\n\u2022 Cashback applies to accessories, mobile devices, and smart life solution purchases in our eShop\"",
  "desc1_fiber": "\"Subscribe to Fiber and open an Orange Money wallet & cash in 1 JD or more to get 10 JD\u2019s Cash Back\"",
  "terms_condition_fiber": "\"1. This offer applies only to the new Fiber subscriptions\n2. To get the Cash Back, customer must open an Orange Money wallet and cash in 1 JD or more in the wallet at the same time of signing the Fiber subscription.\n3. Cashback will be Cashed In to Orange Money Wallet one working week after the Fiber service installation\n4.To get the Cash Back, Orange Money wallet opening and the Fiber service subscription must be during Ramadan\n5.The national number used to open the Orange Money wallet and to subscribe to the Fiber service must be identical to get the Cash Back\n6.Offer valid for the first 2000 customers\n7.Orange Money has the right to stop the campaign at any time.\"",
  "desc1_cash_back": "\"Buy an Orange Postpaid line and open an Orange Money wallet with a 1 JD Cash In or more to get 3JD's Cash Back of the line issuance fees\"",
  "desc3_postpaid": "Open Orange Money wallet and cash in with 5 JD's or more to get 2 JD\u2019s discount on postpaid lines issuance fees \n",
  "terms_cond_postpaid": "\"1.This offer applies to Orange Mobile Postpaid lines sold in Orange Shop\n2. Customer will get a full Cash Back of the line issuance fees\n3.To benefit from this offer, the customer should buy an Orange Postpaid line, open an Orange Money wallet and Cash In 1 JD or more on the same purchased line and within 1 working day we will Cash Back the value of 3 JD\u2019s issuance fees to the customers\u2019 wallet\"",
  "title_ramadan_internet_bundle": "Ramadan Internet Bundle",
  "url_discount_offers": "https://www.orange.jo/EN/orangemoney/Pages/DiscountsAndOffers.aspx",
  "ramadan_talabat": "Get 40% discount on all your Talabat orders when using Orange Money Visa Card & get a weekly chance to win a TV",
  "ramadan_prepaid": "Buy an Orange Prepaid line and open an Orange Money wallet with a 1 JD Cash In or more to get 1 JD Cash Back of the line welcome pack price",
  "terms_comd_visa_card": "\"1. This offer is valid until end of 30/4/2022.\n2. This offer applies to new cards issued only, and in case of applying to replace an existing card for some reason, a fee of 5 JD will be paid.\n3. This campaign includes all Orange Money wallet customers.\n4. Orange Money Visa Card is issued and received through Orange shops located in all Governorates.\n5. Orange Money has the right to stop the campaign at any time and the customers will be notified by text message\n\"",
  "talabat_desc": "\"On the occasion of Ramadan, Orange Money customers will get 40% discount on all purchases from Talabat App when using Orange Money Visa Card & get a weekly chance to win a Sony 55 4k Smart TV.\"",
  "prepaid_desc": "\"Buy an Orange Prepaid line and open an Orange Money wallet with a 1 JD Cash In or more to get 1 JD Cash Back of the line welcome pack price\"",
  "prepaid_cond_charity": "\"1.This offer applies to Orange Mobile Prepaid lines sold in Orange Shops\n2. Customer will get a 1 JD Cash Back of the line welcome pack price: To benefit from this offer, the customer should buy an Orange Prepaid line, open an Orange Money wallet and Cash In 1 JD or more on the same purchased line and within 1 working day we will Cash Back1 JD of the line welcome pack price to the customers\u2019 wallet\"",
