  "terms_cond_talabat": "1. The campaign is valid from 7/4/2022 until the end of 7/5/2022.\n2. This campaign includes all Orange Money Visa cardholders.\n3. There is no minimum transaction amount per order to be eligible to get the discount.\n4. Discount is 40%% of the total order amount.\n5. The maximum discount amount on each order is 3.2 JD.\n6. The customers can get the discount when using Orange Money Visa card only.\n7. Each customer is eligible for two discounts during the campaign period.\n8. The discount includes all purchases executed on Talabat App inside Jordan only.\n9. Customers will get the chance to enter a weekly draw on Sony 55 4k Smart TV.\n10. Orange Money has the right to stop the campaign at any time.\n11. A limited number of customers can benefit from this campaign.\n12. Talabat is responsible for the draw and distributing the prizes",
